[00:00.000]There we sat among the thousand
[00:00.000][by:Murraya_paniculata]
[00:00.000]无数相爱的傻瓜之中，
[00:12.300]fools just like us
[00:12.300]有我们的身影。
[00:17.860]But not so in love like us
[00:17.860]可没人能比我们更加相爱。
[00:24.920]There we spoke of all our feelings
[00:24.920]互通心灵，
[00:35.820]And dreams were born like that
[00:35.820]梦由此产生，
[00:42.740]And we hope for love like that
[00:42.740]这就是我们曾期待的爱情 。
[00:49.770]Now your dreams have changed, we're far apart
[00:49.770]而今你的梦已变，我们已是路人。
[00:52.640]I don't know when or where to start
[00:52.640]我却仍不明白何时何地，
[00:55.230]leading you from my mind
[00:55.230]你开始疏远我的心。
[01:00.300]I want to stand with you again
[01:00.300]想要再与你并肩，
[01:02.490]I hope to find you here again
[01:02.490]想要再次感受到你，
[01:04.530]in the eternal sunshine
[01:04.530]在永恒阳光下的身影 。
[01:09.510]I'll search for the orange moon
[01:09.510]我会一直寻找那橙色的月光 ，
[01:12.250]that lit up our love on the ocean
[01:12.250]来照亮我们爱的海洋，
[01:16.930]while I held your hand
[01:16.930]当我们手挽手。
[01:19.540]Now watch all the waves from the stones
[01:19.540]岩石激起浪花，
[01:23.080]where we gazed to the golden sun
[01:23.080]我们曾在那里仰望灿烂金阳。
[01:29.250]If I see the horizon
[01:29.250]如果能再次见到那闪耀的地平线 ，
[01:32.020]glow just the same as it did when we stood on the hill
[01:32.020]就像曾一同在山上所看到的一样，
[01:39.180]I'll make the arrangements, just wait on that corner for me
[01:39.180]我会有所变化，请在心中为我留出一个角落吧。
[01:49.090]If you drop me a line I'll be sure to make these arrangements
[01:49.090]这一切只要你的一句话。
[01:58.530]Lay your head upon my shoulder
[01:58.530]你的头轻枕我的肩膀，
