[02:16.230]Sweet melodies for thee
[02:16.230]为了心中的你。
[02:23.010]Softly speak to say what I need
[02:23.010]我轻声问，
[02:34.050]Why do you leave
[02:34.050]你为什么要离开，
[02:40.270]My heart is at your feet
[02:40.270]我的心因你而碎。
[02:47.940]Well I'd like to share three words again
[02:47.940]我想要，
[02:51.050]practise these words with you again
[02:51.050]再对你说出那三个字，
[02:53.720]if you think is possible
[02:53.720]如果你认为为时不晚。
[02:58.570]and maybe I can pull you close
